                                <TextBlock Text="What it does: Automatically crawls the website, discovers forms and input fields, tests for SQL injection, and attempts to find persistent storage vulnerabilities (like comment systems, user profiles)" Foreground="#C9D1D9" TextWrapping="Wrap" LineHeight="22" Margin="0,0,0,6"/>
